# 🌍 Bulk Auto Geo-Tagger Pro (Enterprise Local SEO Engine)

An advanced, interactive Python-based automation suite designed for SEO professionals to bulk-inject deep EXIF metadata and GPS coordinates into local business images. Built to scale local SEO and dominate Google Map Packs.

## ✨ Key Features
* **Interactive Dual-Mode Engine:** * *Mode 1:* Auto-converts WebP/PNG to JPG for full Windows Properties visibility.
  * *Mode 2:* Retains original formats (WebP/PNG/JPG) while deep-injecting EXIF data for Google Bots.
* **Smart Multi-Folder Routing:** Organize your campaigns by city or area. The script crawls infinite sub-folders, applying specific location data from a single `details.txt` file per main folder.
* **Ultimate EXIF Injection:** Embeds Latitude, Longitude, Keywords, Author, Copyright, and highly detailed descriptions.
* **Authority Spoofing:** Auto-assigns 5-Star Ratings, fresh "Time Digitized" stamps, and professional Camera Make/Model (e.g., Canon EOS 5D) to maximize image authority.

